<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF9F6A21FA499B191B12BABA" lastPageId="101" lastPageNumber="859" pageId="100" pageNumber="858" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF9F6A21FA499B191B12BABA" blockId="100.[1459,2667,2446,3465]" lastBlockId="101.[123,1328,280,514]" lastPageId="101" lastPageNumber="859" pageId="100" pageNumber="858">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF9F6A20FA499B191913B653" bold="true" box="[1461,1811,3392,3425]" pageId="100" pageNumber="858">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. Seems to be a rare species, with an extent of occurrence under 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFF9F6A20F7609B351713B6BB" box="[2204,2323,3436,3465]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="100" pageNumber="858" unit="km" value="1000.0">1000 km</quantity>
?, and known only from two nearby localities, located in a highly restricted protected area. The major threat 1s extensive habitat loss caused by conversion to agriculture; moreover, natural forces such as tropical storms and possibly hurricanes can also negatively affect the region.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
